  <archetypedescription>     
    <p>
      Hedge Wizards are wandering mages of little raw talent, they make their money
      in side shows, by grifting, in displays of magics for the entertainment of young
      children and by providing mystic readings for housewives and the love-lorn.
    </p>

    <figure>
      <img src="./resources/archetypes/hedge_wizard/the_crooked_staff_by_dw_miller_by_conceptsbymiller-day36nr.png"
	   scale="0.58"/>
    </figure>        

    <p>
      Not displaying enough ability to be considered a threat, Hedge wizards are usually
      left to their own business. They are however required to be licensed as users of
      magick and produce said license upon request from the law.
    </p>
  </archetypedescription>

